<p>Has sent JDD a copy of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>; knows it will horrify him, but hopes JDD will credit him with an honest search for truth. Believes that JDD may come to think there is more to be said "in favour of mutability of species than is at first appreciated".</p> 
